<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> When granting a loan to an undertaking or to a body other than a Member State, the Bank shall make the loan conditional either on a guarantee from the Member State in whose territory the project will be carried out or on other adequate guarantees. </inglise>
