<eesti> a) intressitulud laenudelt, mis pank on andnud liikmesriikide poolt vastavalt artiklile 5 makstavatest summadest; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) interest received on loans granted by the Bank out of funds derived from repayment of the loans referred to in (a); </inglise>
