<eesti> Ta v&otilde;ib siiski lepingutes m&auml;&auml;ratleda konkreetse aadressi v&otilde;i n&auml;ha ette vahekohtumenetluse. </eesti>
<inglise> The property and assets of the Bank shall not be liable to attachment or to seizure by way of execution except by decision of a court. </inglise>
<eesti> Panga omandit ja varasid saab ainult kohtu otsusega arestida v&otilde;i allutada sundt&auml;itmisele. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 30 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 30 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The Board of Governors may, acting unanimously, decide to establish a European Investment Fund, which shall have legal personality and financial autonomy, and of which the Bank shall be a founding member. </inglise>
<eesti> Juhatajate n&otilde;ukogu v&otilde;ib teha &uuml;heh&auml;&auml;lselt otsuse asutada Euroopa InvesteERI-misfond, millel on iseseisev &otilde;igusv&otilde;ime ja mis on majanduslikult iseseisev ning mille asutajaliikmeks on pank. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The Board of Governors shall establish the Statute of the European Investment Fund by unanimous decision. </inglise>
<eesti> Juhatajate n&otilde;ukogu kinnitab &uuml;heh&auml;&auml;lse otsusega Euroopa Investeerimisfondi p&otilde;hikirja. </eesti>
<inglise> The Statute shall define, in particular, its objectives, structure, capital, membership, financial resources, means of intervention and auditing arrangements, as well as the relationship between the organs of the Bank and those of the Fund. </inglise>
<eesti> P&otilde;hikiri m&auml;&auml;ratleb eelk&otilde;ige fondi eesm&auml;rgid, struktuuri, kapitali, liikmeskonna, finantsressursid, sekkumisvahendid ja auditeerimiskorra, samuti panga organite ja fondi organite omavahelised suhted. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Notwithstanding the provisions of Article 20(2), the Bank shall be entitled to participate in the management of the Fund and contribute to its subscribed capital up to the amount determined by the Board of Governors acting unanimously. </inglise>
<eesti> Pangal on artikli 20 l&otilde;ike 2 s&auml;tetest olenemata &otilde;igus osaleda fondi juhtimises ja m&auml;rgitud kapitalis juhatajate n&otilde;ukogu poolt &uuml;heh&auml;&auml;lselt m&auml;&auml;ratud summa ulatuses. </eesti>
<inglise> 4. </inglise>
<eesti> 4. </eesti>
<inglise> The European Community may become a member of the Fund and contribute to its subscribed capital. </inglise>
<eesti> Euroopa &Uuml;hendus v&otilde;ib saada fondi liikmeks ja osaleda tema m&auml;rgitud kapitalis. </eesti>
<inglise> Financial institutions with an interest in the objectives of the Fund may be invited to become members. </inglise>
<eesti> Fondi eesm&auml;rkidest huvituvaid rahaasutusi v&otilde;ib kutsuda fondi liikmeks. </eesti>
<inglise> 5. </inglise>
<eesti> 5. </eesti>
<inglise> The Protocol on the privileges and immunities of the European Communities shall apply to the Fund, to the members of its organs in the performance of their duties as such and to its staff. </inglise>
<eesti> Euroopa &uuml;henduste privileegide ja immuniteetide protokolli kohaldatakse fondi suhtes, tema organite liikmete suhtes nende vastavate kohustuste t&auml;itmisel ja tema t&ouml;&ouml;tajate suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise> The Fund shall in addition be exempt from any form of taxation or imposition of a like nature on the occasion of any increase in its capital and from the various formalities which may be connected therewith in the State where the Fund has its seat. </inglise>
<eesti> Peale selle on fond vabastatud mis tahes kujul maksustamisest v&otilde;i muust sellelaadsest kohustusest tema kapitali suurenemise korral ning mitmesugustest formaalsustest, mida v&otilde;idakse sellega siduda riigis, kus on k&otilde;nealuse fondi alaline asukoht. </eesti>
<inglise> Similarly, its dissolution or liquidation shall not give rise to any imposition. </inglise>
<eesti> Samamoodi ei tulene mingeid makse fondi tegevuse l&otilde;petamisest v&otilde;i likvideerimisest. </eesti>
<inglise> Finally, the activities of the Fund and of its organs carried out in accordance with its Statute shall not be subject to any turnover tax. </inglise>
<eesti> L&otilde;puks ei kuulu k&auml;ibemaksu alla fondi ja tema organite tegevus, mis on koosk&otilde;las tema p&otilde;hikirjaga. </eesti>
<inglise> Those dividends, capital gains or other forms of revenue stemming from the Fund to which the members, other than the European Community and the Bank, are entitled, shall however remain subject to the fiscal provisions of the applicable legislation. </inglise>
<eesti> Nende fondist saadavate dividendide, kapitali kasvutulude v&otilde;i muud liiki tulude suhtes, millele teistel liikmetel peale Euroopa &Uuml;henduse ja panga on &otilde;igus, kehtivad kohaldatavate &otilde;igusaktide maksus&auml;tted. </eesti>
<inglise> 6. </inglise>
<eesti> 6. </eesti>
<inglise> The Court of Justice shall, within the limits hereinafter laid down, have jurisdiction in disputes concerning measures adopted by organs of the Fund. </inglise>
<eesti> Edaspidi s&auml;testatud piirides on Euroopa Kohtu p&auml;devuses vaidlused, mis k&auml;sitlevad fondi organite v&otilde;etud meetmeid. </eesti>
<inglise> Proceedings against such measures may be instituted by any member of the Fund in its capacity as such or by Member States under the conditions laid down in Article 173 of this Treaty. </inglise>
<eesti> Selliste meetmete vastu v&otilde;ib iga fondi liige oma erip&auml;ra v&otilde;i liikmesriik k&auml;esoleva lepingu artiklis 230 s&auml;testatud tingimuste alusel algatada kohtuasja. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Rome this twenty-fifth day of March in the year one thousand nine hundred and fifty-seven. </inglise>
<eesti> S&otilde;lmitud kahek&uuml;mne viiendal m&auml;rtsil tuhande &uuml;heksasaja viiek&uuml;mne seitsmendal aastal Roomas. </eesti>
 